FinancialInstitutionDocumentForm is a Form
    is primary
    propagate as a drill
    title is "Document"
    Layout
        paragraph
            FinancialInstitution
                display as text
            FinancialInstitution.Description
                no label
                display as text
        single column
            Description
        paragraph
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                Attachment.Title
            Attachment.File
